Package net.bitnine.agensgraph.ext.agtype

Class Agtype

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.postgresql.util.PGobject
      • net.bitnine.agensgraph.ext.agtype.Agtype
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable
    public class Agtype
extends org.postgresql.util.PGobject
implements Cloneable
    Stores values of various kinds in a single object for use in PostgreSQL. The text representation is built on top of the JSON format specification. The goal of the text representation is making it compatible with JSON as much as possible so that valid JSON values can be parsed without effort.

    Valid Agtypes:
    • null
    • int
    • long
    • double
    • boolean
    • String
    • AgtypeList
    • AgtypeMap
    Since:
    0.0.1
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
